---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy | Triangle Dehumidifiers"
  description="Privacy policy for Triangle Dehumidifiers, LLC. Learn how we collect, use, and protect your information."
  canonical="/privacy"
>
  <section class="svc-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p>Last updated: January 2025</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container" style="max-width: 760px;">
      <h2>Overview</h2>
      <p>
        Triangle Dehumidifiers, LLC ("we," "us," or "our") operates the website
        triangledehumidifiers.com. This privacy policy explains how we collect, use, and protect
        information you provide when using our website or contacting us.
      </p>

      <h2 style="margin-top: 2rem;">Information We Collect</h2>
      <p>We collect information you voluntarily provide, including:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Name, phone number, and email address submitted through our contact form</li>
        <li>Your city or location within our service area</li>
        <li>Messages or descriptions you provide about your situation</li>
      </ul>
      <p>
        We may also collect standard website analytics data (pages visited, time on site, browser
        type) through third-party analytics tools. This data is aggregated and not linked to
        individual users.
      </p>

      <h2 style="margin-top: 2rem;">How We Use Your Information</h2>
      <p>Information you submit is used exclusively to:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Respond to your inquiry or service request</li>
        <li>Schedule evaluations or follow-up consultations</li>
        <li>Communicate information relevant to your specific situation</li>
      </ul>
      <p>
        We do not sell, rent, or share your personal information with third parties for marketing
        purposes.
      </p>

      <h2 style="margin-top: 2rem;">Data Retention</h2>
      <p>
        Contact form submissions and correspondence are retained for the period necessary to fulfill
        the service request and for reasonable record-keeping purposes. You may request deletion of
        your information by contacting us directly.
      </p>

      <h2 style="margin-top: 2rem;">Cookies</h2>
      <p>
        This website may use standard browser cookies for basic functionality and analytics. Cookies
        do not contain personal information. You may disable cookies in your browser settings; this
        will not prevent you from using any part of this website.
      </p>

      <h2 style="margin-top: 2rem;">Third-Party Links</h2>
      <p>
        This website may contain links to external websites. We are not responsible for the privacy
        practices of those sites and encourage you to review their policies independently.
      </p>

      <h2 style="margin-top: 2rem;">Contact Us</h2>
      <p>
        If you have questions about this privacy policy or wish to request deletion of your
        information, contact us at:
      </p>
      <p>
        Triangle Dehumidifiers, LLC<br />
        <a href="tel:9195550123">(919) 555-0123</a><br />
        <a href="mailto:info@triangledehumidifiers.com">info@triangledehumidifiers.com</a>
      </p>

      <h2 style="margin-top: 2rem;">Changes to This Policy</h2>
      <p>
        We may update this privacy policy periodically. Changes will be reflected on this page with
        an updated date. Continued use of our website following any changes constitutes acceptance
        of the updated policy.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
